	<p>Aye, they'd have to rework ldon raiding for sure.  Just throwing the general concept out there to see how the casual players would feel about it.  The idea that you can join an 18 man pickup raid for a 2 hour "easy" raid, earn raid points, and eventually buy VT loot with those points.  Or slightly more planning and coordination, join an 18 man hard ldon raid, earn hard ldon points, and buy an EP piece eventually.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
